Syntax: %bSTATS <option>%b

Outputs various statistics depending on %b<option>%b.
Options:
   %bO%b           - Display users who have access to %O
   %bB%b           - Display TCM bot lines
   %bS%b           - Display server link lines
   %bU%b           - Display current uptime
   %bM%b           - Display memory usage
   %bI%b           - Display restricted hostmasks
   %bG%b           - Display active glines
   %bJ%b           - Display active jupes
   %bP%b           - Display port lines
   %bC%b           - Display monitored channels
   %b?%b           - Display SendK and RecieveK
